Tacitus (Hist. ll. 86) says oi him: non tam praemiis periculorum - quam ipsis periculis laetus. He led an expedition against the Dacians in 86. The army was surprised anddeieated,and Fuscus was slain; Tac. Agr. 41; Suet. Dum. 6.
